data.description: If you are looking for superlative location, look no further. This home is it! Priced to sell and ready for you creative vision. Two levels with formal living and dining room.  Powder room on main level with two spacious bedrooms and one full bath upstairs. Just a few blocks to The Capitol and Historic Eastern Market that's loaded with  shops and restaurants on Barracks Row. Just a block and a half away from the largest park in Capitol Hill, Lincoln Park. A half block North is one of Washington DC's Highest rated public schools Maury Elementary (which received 9-10 stars from great schools)This home has all the potential. Truly must see!!
